				<div id="post-11326" class="post-11326 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-survival-preparedness tag-lifestyle-planning">
					<h1 class="entry-title">Episode-1274- 14 Life Rules of a Modern Survivalist</h1>

					<div class="entry-meta">
						<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/rules-of-a-modern-survivalist" title="1:19 pm" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">January 7, 2014</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/rules-of-a-modern-survivalist#comments" title="Comment on Episode-1274- 14 Life Rules of a Modern Survivalist">34 Comments</a></span>
											</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

					<div class="entry-content">
						<div id="tweetbutton11326" class="tw_button" style="float:right;margin-left:10px;"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Frules-of-a-modern-survivalist&amp;text=Episode-1274-%2014%20Life%20Rules%20of%20a%20Modern%20Survivalist&amp;related=&amp;lang=en&amp;count=horizontal&amp;counturl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Frules-of-a-modern-survivalist" class="twitter-share-button"  style="width:55px;height:22px;background:transparent url('http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-tweet-button/tweetn.png') no-repeat  0 0;text-align:left;text-indent:-9999px;display:block;">Tweet</a></div><div class="podPress_content podPress_content_audio_mp3">
<div class="podpress_playerspace podpress_playerspace_audio_mp3 podpress_mp3player" style="display:block;" ><div id="podPressPlayerSpace_1"><!-- podPress --></div></div>
<div class="podPress_downloadlinks podPress_downloadlinks_audio_mp3"><a href="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2014/1-14/epi-1274-14-life-rules-of-modernsurvival.mp3" target="new" title="Download: Episode-1274- 14 Life Rules of a Modern Survivalist" class="podpress_downloadimglink podpress_downloadimglink_audio_mp3"><img src="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress/images/audio_mp3_button.png" class="podPress_imgicon podpress_imgicon_audio_mp3" alt="" /></a> <span class="podpress_mediafile_title podpress_mediafile_title_audio_mp3">Episode-1274- 14 Life Rules of a Modern Survivalist</span> <span class="podpress_mediafile_dursize podpress_mediafile_dursize_audio_mp3">[ 1:35:34 ]</span> <a href="#podPressPlayerSpace_1" class="podpress_playlink podpress_playlink_audio_mp3" onclick="javascript:podPressShowHidePlayer('1', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2014/1-14/epi-1274-14-life-rules-of-modernsurvival.mp3', 290, 24, 'false', 'http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress/images/vpreview_center.png', 'Episode-1274- 14 Life Rules of a Modern Survivalist', 'The Survival Podcast'); return false;"><span id="podPressPlayerSpace_1_PlayLink" class="podPress_playerspace_playlink">Play Now</span></a><input type="hidden" id="podPressPlayerSpace_1_OrigURL" value="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2014/1-14/epi-1274-14-life-rules-of-modernsurvival.mp3" /> | <a href="#podPressPlayerSpace_1" class="podpress_playinpopup podpress_playinpopup_audio_mp3" onclick="javascript:podPressPopupPlayer('1', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2014/1-14/epi-1274-14-life-rules-of-modernsurvival.mp3', 290, 24, 'The Survival Podcast', '11326', 'Episode-1274- 14 Life Rules of a Modern Survivalist', 'The Survival Podcast'); return false;">Play in Popup</a> | <a href="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2014/1-14/epi-1274-14-life-rules-of-modernsurvival.mp3" target="new" class="podpress_downloadlink podpress_downloadlink_audio_mp3">Download</a></div></div>
<script type="text/javascript">podPressShowHidePlayer('1', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2014/1-14/epi-1274-14-life-rules-of-modernsurvival.mp3', 290, 24, 'false', 'http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress/images/vpreview_center.png', 'Episode-1274- 14 Life Rules of a Modern Survivalist', 'The Survival Podcast');</script><p>I was going to call this show &#8220;14 Rules for Being a Modern Survivalist&#8221; but I realized that would violate my survival tenet that reads&#8230;</p>
<p>&#8220;Your personal philosophy is more important for you than mine! You are the master of your own life and if you don’t agree with my views, great, define, understand and implement your own. The biggest thing you can do is understand that you are in control of your life and that what you do matters. Those two factors have the greatest impact on individual survival across every demographic you can imagine.&#8221;</p>
<p>For me that is a deep intrinsic belief not just a tenet of modern <a title="survival philosophy" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/modern-survival-philosophy">survival philosophy</a>.  I may come across as fully convinced in my beliefs and passionate about them to the extreme but that doesn&#8217;t mean I wish to impose them on any other person.  So I decided I would simply let you guys know today about 10 of the &#8220;rules&#8221; that I follow in my life.  Some are very old for me, they have guided me since childhood, others I have gained in recent years on my walk as a modern survivalist&#8230;</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #800000;">Join Me Today As I Discuss&#8230;</span></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Ignore politicians, do not however ignore their actions and resulting consequences</li>
<li>Truly understand in this order absolute needs, needs, comfort items, luxuries</li>
<li>Use anything that works, as long as it is ethical and actually works</li>
<li>Solve any problem you see in your head even if you can&#8217;t implement the solution</li>
<li>Be concerned with the survival of others, not just your own survival</li>
<li>Ask what if like a child, answer that question like an adult</li>
<li>Be extremely grateful to be alive in this time in history</li>
<li>Never violate your personal moral code of ethics</li>
<li>Never be led by fear specifically fear of losing something you don&#8217;t even have yet</li>
<li>Take pride in your phyical abilities but depend on your mental abilities</li>
<li>Learn from everything you do, the good, the bad and the failures</li>
<li>Never accept that things are simply just the way they are</li>
<li>Never feel you have anything coming to you and be grateful for what does</li>
<li>Never waste a minute on the past, live in the now and in the tomorrow</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><span style="color: #800000;">Resources for today’s show…</span></strong></p>
<ul>
