		<div class="comment-author vcard">
			<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/e324d9b595febe29f5f80da408da2ec2?s=48&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />
